                    <span>I have been a huge fan of Alan's for years. And I didn't buy this book because of its high price for years. Well, then I broke down and bought it. Used in conjunctions with Alan's other strategies, this book landed me a $100,000 deal. When I asked what made the difference, they said, "The proposal." Enough said. Buy it. Use it. Profit from it.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Use this book to make money today!</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
                      <span>5</span>
